Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:04.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｴﾙ)あのとき\N助けられなくて ごめんなさい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I wasn't able to help you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)お前も俺に謝るのか｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're apologizing to me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:10.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が謝ることなど 何もない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:13.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)\Nたとえ この命を失おうとも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I should lose my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 陛下の真意を知りたいのだ｡\N頼む｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I must know His Majesty's intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾌｧﾊﾞﾛ･ﾚｵｰﾈ)お前が\N何を隠しててもかまわねぇが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you think hard before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく考えて選択しろよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオスが好きなんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You love Charioce, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:44.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾄﾞ)ガブリエル様はどう？\N何を言っても反応しない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Lady Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't responded to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閉じこもったままだ｡\Nエルに続いて ジャンヌ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's locked herself in her chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First El, then Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:52.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに ソフィエル様も\N去ってしまうなんて…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now even Lady Sofiel has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)ソフィエル…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sofiel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(肉屋の妻)やだねぇ｡\N(肉屋)しょうがねぇだろ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最近じゃ テロが頻発してるし｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrorism has been rampant lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:26.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ それに 脱獄犯が\Nまだ隠れてるかもしんねぇんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fugitives could still be hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日の晩も おっかねぇ赤い竜が\N飛び回ってたし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There was that scary red dragon\Nflying around last night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が終わっても\N落ち着かないなぁ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When are things going to finally\Nsettle down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王宮じゃ\N今晩 舞踏会だってさ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently there's gonna be a ball\Nat the palace tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お偉いさんたちは\Nこんなときも華やかでいいねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice that the aristocrats\Ncan still enjoy themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:46.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(子供)待ってよ｡\Nパパパッ… パーン！(花火の音)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪パーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sofiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:57.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ソフィエル様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:59.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)居所は まだ分からない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have not found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The many soldiers on patrol are making\Nthis difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)\N兵の数も多く 難航している｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What information is there on Nina or Bacchus?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナやバッカスたちの\N情報も何も？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:13.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もない｡\Nあったのは ゆうべ 竜が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The only information I managed to hear were just rumors\Nof a dragon flying over Anatae last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:17.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナテｨ上空を飛び回っていたとの\Nうわさくらいだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:20.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その竜の色は？\N(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)色？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What color was the dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Color?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they said it was red.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か 赤かったとの話だ｡\Nニーナ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？\N(ｼﾞｬﾝﾇ)ニーナは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is dragonfolk, and she's\Nable to transform into a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い竜に変身する\N竜族の娘なのです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いします\N私も行かせてください｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Let me go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エルは\Nニーナと一緒にいるはずです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,El is probably with Nina and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be fewer soldiers once\Nthe sun goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:48.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日が落ちれば 兵の数が減る｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のそばを離れないなら…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you promise not\Nto leave my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the same\Nand lose themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz there are lots of roads to go\NAnd the path suddenly seems rougher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna walk straight ahead\NKnock down another dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Most broke before they ever came true
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on the way you think it\NTo a yielding heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the future, hope,\Ndespair and worry all look all the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that you'll turn down the truth\Nthat lied to you that day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were prepared for it all.\NYou go your way, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But walk this way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:36.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パーン！ パパパッ… パーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ･回想)((いい？ まずは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Nina and the aristocrat boy\Nwill infiltrate the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴族の坊やとニーナが\N王宮に潜入する))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)((あっ？))\N(ﾘﾀ)((王宮内に潜入して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you locate the king inside the palace,\Nyou will stand by and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王様を見つけたら 近くで待機｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アフロは\Nそこのおっきいおじさんと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Afro and the big guy there will infiltrate the palace\Nfrom the knights' barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎士団の宿舎側から 王宮に潜入))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:44.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)((カイザルは団長だったし\Nアザゼルは悪魔で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Kaisar was the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel is a demon, and the drunk is a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酔っ払いは神でしょ？))\N(ﾊﾝｻ)((クワァ～))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)((あんたが\Nやるしかないじゃない))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That just leaves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)((確クワァに))\N((はぁ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, once we confirm Afro is in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)((で ｱﾌﾛの潜入が確認できたら\N私が合図を送るわ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしたら\Nあなたは 竜になりなさい))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you transform into a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)((暴れるの？))\N(ﾘﾀ)((暴れちゃダメ))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I get to smash things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((混乱すれば それでいいから｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need them confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You will steal the king's bracelet in the confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:08.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その混乱に乗じて\N王から腕輪を奪って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and then climb on Nina's back\Nto escape from the terrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナの背中に乗って\Nテラスから脱出しなさい))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((そんなに うまくいくか？))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it really go that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)((ニーナが竜になれば\N心配ないわ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina will be fine as long as she transforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((俺は？))\N((安心しなさい➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,捕まったら\Nまた 牢獄に迎えに行くから｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get caught, we'll break you\Nout of prison again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For the rest of you, on the off chance\Nthe escape plan fails,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りのメンバーは 万が一 うまく\N脱出できなかったときのために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:30.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出経路の確保と 追っ手が\Nかかったときに備えてもらうわ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you're to secure the escape routes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and engage any pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ ﾊﾝｻ ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)((うん))\N(ｴﾙ)((僕も王宮に行く))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go to the palace as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:39.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)((あなたは\N漆黒兵が現れたときのために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be standing by near the escape route
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出経路で待機してもらうわ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in case the Onyx Soldiers appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アザゼル あんたが面倒見なさい))\N((でも…))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel, you watch after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, this plan isn't the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:58.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((正直 勢いだけの作戦｡\N何が起きるか分からないわ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((むちゃは禁物よ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So nobody be reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This plan hinges on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:09.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この作戦は 私に懸かってる｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)へっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:15.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)\Nったく 何してんのよ あの子は｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)それにしても お嬢さん➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the young lady
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed very eager to be the one to\Ninfiltrate the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,随分 王宮に潜入する役を\Nやりたがってましたねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:25.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)くぅ～！ どうせ\N王宮料理が食べたかったんだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably wants to eat the palace food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だといいけど…｡\Nあっちは順調かしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫パーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ ご苦労｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:46.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)慣れた様子だな｡\Nまあな｡ これでも 昔➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-You look right at home.\N-I suppose I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not look it, but I used to be a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:49.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎士の称号ってやつを\Nもらったことあるんだぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:53.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは１０年前のことか？\Nああ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, along with that captain of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの団長さんと一緒にな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:59.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒュー… パーン パパン！\N(花火の音)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-This appears to be it.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)ここだな｡\Nああ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:12.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 行ってくる｡\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)ああ 任せた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～ そうだ\N逃げ道の確保は よろしく頼むぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you guys to secure\Nour escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん あいつは竜になれない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably won't be able to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？ どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)((我ら漆黒兵➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Onyx Soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての命は 王であるあなたに\Nささげております｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,offer our lives to serve Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうか 使命の遂行に専念を))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:48.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫コンコン(ﾉｯｸ)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)入れ｡\N≫ガチャ バタン(ﾄﾞｱの開閉音)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(侍従)陛下\N間もなく舞踏会の時間です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is almost time for the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お気持ちは分かりますが\N先の戦の復興ままならぬ現状➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but with the uncertainty of the coming war,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:08.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,資金集めの催しも\N王の重要な責務であります｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,fund-raising events are an important\Npart of a king's duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わあ～｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっごい！ うん よし｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nへっ？ あっ ちょっ… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ｡ お前\Nそんなことしてっと怪しまれるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, cut that out!\NPeople will get suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで？ 食べてるだけじゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? I'm just eating here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ん…｡\Nいいから よせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪(貴族)おお～ これは これは｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)えっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't the young Visponti lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴィスポンティ家の\Nｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ坊ちゃんじゃありませんか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へえ～ このような場で\Nお会いするのは 久しぶりですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it has been a while since we last\Nsaw you at an event like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～ うん まあ…\Nはははっ… どうも｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？ こちらの女性は？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might this young lady be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:05.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nあっ えっと こちらの女性は…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フィアンセです｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)んっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm his fiance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:13.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そうですか｡\Nすてきな女性ですねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a lovely girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ～ら\Nありがとうございます～｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)あぁ…｡\Nん？ どした？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(貴族たち)おお～｡\N(貴族)陛下だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(貴族)シャリオス王…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alland.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ アレンドさん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nまさか それは 俺のことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those girls doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの女の人たちは 何してんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)あれは\N王に誘ってもらうのを待ってんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're waiting for the king's invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:05.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誘ってもらうって何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Invitation for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ダンスだ｡\Nあっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)あっ｡ お… おい\Nちょっと 待て待て 待て待て｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whoa! Hold up, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is King Charioce going to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シャリオス王が踊るのか？\N初めて見ました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, didn't it seem like the girl\Nwas the one to invite him to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というか 今 あの女性から\N誘ってませんでした？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nあいつ どういうつもりだよ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man! Your fiance just asked\Nthe king to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坊ちゃん あなたのフィアンセが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王を踊りに誘ってますが…｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ああ… あれ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, that's actually my younger sister.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は妹っす｡\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:28.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)な～にがどうなったら\N王様と踊ることになるのかしらね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now how in the world did she end up\Ndancing with the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ぶぅ～！\N(ﾊﾝｻ)クワァ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen that kind of dance before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなダンスもあるんだね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前 一緒に踊ったのも\N楽しかったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we danced together\Nwas fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきのも すごいすてき｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but this was really nice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(心の声)≪あっ いけない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. There was something\NI was supposed to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:41.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪聞かなきゃいけないことが\Nあるんだった≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話がある｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪きた！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Does your stomach hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どしたの？ おなか痛いの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっと… 怒ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ わ… 私 なんかしちゃった？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう会うことはできない｡\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前とは もう会うことはできない\N二度とな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ… えっ 何言ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dedicated my life to\Nfulfilling my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余は 王の責務を果たすことに\Nこの身をささげた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:30.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから それを\N今日 教えてくれるんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, weren't you going to tell me about that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:33.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には関係のないことだ｡\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:44.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしちゃったの？\Nさっきは踊ってくれたのに…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You just danced with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときはキスしてくれたのに｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you kissed me that time before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you lying when you said that you\Nwere going to tell me everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:56.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に 全部話してくれる\Nって言ったのは うそだったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:00.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ 全部うそだ｡\Nうそに決まっているだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…｡\N去れ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去らぬなら 兵を呼び 捕らえるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, I will call the\Nguards to seize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫おいおい ひでぇ男だな あんた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, talk about a terrible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなんでも 俺の弟子なんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still my student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんまり\N傷つけねぇでくんねぇかな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… 師匠｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hand over that bracelet of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左手に着けた腕輪をよこしな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは\N一度着けたら 死ぬまで取れん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once worn, it can't be taken off\Nas long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 悪ぃけど 腕 切り落とすか\N死んでもらうぜ 王様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, sorry, you're either gonna have to\Nget your arm chopped off or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ～！\Nどっ… おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,撃っちゃダメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:10.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがよ ニーナ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nina,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:14.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その王様は これからも\N大量に殺すかもしれないぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that king might go on to kill a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも ダメ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I shoot you and\Nkill Charioce?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ お前を撃って\Nシャリオスを殺すのはどうだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だあっ！ はぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余興は これまでだ｡\N間もなく兵が来る｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This charade ends here.\NThe guards shall arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:56.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな｡\N今夜は おいとまさせてもらうぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we never dance together again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 一緒に踊れないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない 二度とな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ｡\Nバキッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to hurt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,傷つけんなって言ったろ 王様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mr. King...\N-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)動くな！\N(兵士)陛下 ご無事ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we took too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちと のんびりし過ぎちまったか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)おい 立て｡\N待て｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:42.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)陛下｡\Nへへっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボォン！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)失敗よ｡ みんなに合図して！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan failed! Signal everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ソフィエル様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sofiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,坊ちゃん｡ 妹君が\N渦中に巻き込まれていますよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man! Your sister seems to be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh! I'm going to go help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:14.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\Nえっ？ あっ た… 助けてきます｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)捜せ！\N(兵士)まだ遠くへは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't have gotten far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行ってないはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(兵士)裏を固めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Secure the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)賊は まだ王宮にいる！\N逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The bandits are still in the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let them get away!\N-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was a beautiful performance.\N-Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:36.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名演技だ｡\N急げ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you can be depressed later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ へこむのは あとだ｡\N今は逃げねぇと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to run now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠\N私 フラれちゃった｡ ははっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I just got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We need to focus on getting away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:53.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠の言うとおり\N今は早く逃げないと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)こっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ちょい ちょい！\N速すぎるっつぅの！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!\NYou're too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:13.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何があった？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never getting involved with them ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらに関わるのは\Nもう御免だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ… 家に帰ろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'm going home.\N-Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)どこへ行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)えっ？\Nあっ あの～ 道に迷いまして…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スラムは こっちだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The slums are this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne D'Arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ･ダルク｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…｡\Nお母さん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As horrible as you are\NI can't help but love you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while I waited\NThat is all I felt
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ephemeral lovers, both flawed and missing pieces\NWe have finally become one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in this miniature garden at the edge of sorrow\NCan you hear my heart speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:22:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I may no longer feel\Nthat I want to go back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are feelings, feelings, feelings\NI can only feel now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to run away with you, dancing\Njust like in a fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it will only be this once, darling\NI am on the same ark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.32,0:22:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sha-ra-ran-la, Sha-ra-ran-la\NCinderella step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～！ ニーナ 待て！\Nタッタッタッ…(足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ… 待てって！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ！\Nボォン！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:06.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バキッ！\Nドサッ！(倒れる音)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！\Nバキッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:12.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドサッ！\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:16.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐぐっ…｡ くそっ｡\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)そんな小細工が\Nいつまでも通用すると思うな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We have seen enough of your tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:23.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,師匠～！\N来るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.32,0:23:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back! Run, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.35,0:23:25.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げろ ニーナ！\Nえっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:36.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(竜人)お前が赤い竜か？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are the red dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:40.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(竜人)ここで死んでもらう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.92,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You will die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.01,0:23:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Charioce XVII's morning starts early.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What could he be pondering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Rage of Bahamut:\NVirgin Soul, "From Heaven to Hell."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- First, we must eat some meat.\N- You must really like it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.19,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,BAHA SOUL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Baha Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch next time too!
